𝐌𝐄𝐄𝐓 𝐘𝐎𝐔𝐑 𝐋𝐀𝐒𝐇 & 𝐁𝐑𝐎𝐖 𝐓𝐄𝐂𝐇 ⚡️

Hi girls! I thought I’d come on here to introduce myself as I’ve gained a few followers over the past few months! 🥰

My name is Iasmina, I’m 21 years old and I’ve been in the beauty industry for 5 years now! I’m passionate about providing high quality treatments and making sure my clients leave with a smile on their face. 

During my studies, I decided to do a lash course. I immediately fell in love with the treatment and the socialising aspect that came with lashing. Coming towards the end of 6th form I knew I wanted to try run my own business in the beauty industry. I then did up my garage to have my own home salon (some you of you may remember when I used to do lashes in my bedroom 🫣). 

Fast forward 5 years later I’m now offering a wider range of treatments, have managed to be fully booked each week and have met the most amazing clients along the way. I’m so lucky to be able to call this my job. 🥹

I am so grateful to have such supportive followers and loyal clients that I’ve met along the way. I cannot believe the growth I’ve achieved over the past year which makes me even more excited for what’s to come in the future! I would not have been able to accomplish this without the support from all of you. 🫶💕💌

Massive thank you to @flashinmemories for the shoot!! Cannot wait to show you the rest of the pics 😉

latestPosts.caption:
I cannot stress how important it is for brow lamination clients to regularly use a brow oil or serum. Without regular oiling, your eye brows can get extremely dry and the lamination won’t hold.‼️

What should I be using? 🤔
Look for an aftercare oil made with natural nourishing ingredients like castor/ vitamin e / argan oil. These are rich in vitamins to hydrate the hairs and promote hair growth. 

I do sell castor oil & vitamin bottles which you can purchase at your appointment for £5 ( what I used in the video above) 

If you would like to purchase a bottle from a good brand , I’ve listed below what I’d recommend 🫶
- @saintandserenity silk drops 18.99
- @officialnavyprofessional lash and brow conditioning serum- £16.99
- @lashbase_uk lifted lash and brow oil £6.99

If you have any questions on brow lamination aftercare please message me!

. Arrive on time!! ⏰- any lateness can result in your appointment getting cancelled as I’m back to back and can’t run over. Parking has been awful down my road recently but please try and park your car anywhere as long as your not blocking any driveways.
